column5: Na, there hasn't been any mention of large quantities of food and beer missing and it wasn't found passed out under bench with its head stuck in a pic-in-nic basket.
BWAHAHAHAHA  Now thats funny.  Sorry Boss, but it was.
I do see some similarities though so it could be a relative.
Get out of town Boo Boo!

We were heading up hwy 11 on Friday on our way to yet another "Weekend at Bernie's. It was mid morning and as we were just outside of Huntsville, I spotted a black bear sitting just off the side of the road, watching the traffic go by! Seemed a little out of place, but a neat thing to see anyway. HH
